{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-123456789abc",
    "name": "Ecommerce EDA MFE",
    "description": "Full system collection for the Ecommerce EDA MFE platform.\n\nServices:\n- **API Gateway** — :8080 (Phase 3 ✅)\n- **Product Service** — :8081 (Phase 2 ✅)\n- **Order Service** — :8082 (Phase 6 ✅)\n- **Recommendations AI Service** — :8083 (Phase 7 ✅)\n\nPrerequisites:\n1. `docker compose -f docker-compose.infra.yml up -d` from repo root (includes Ollama + llama3.2 pull)\n2. Start the relevant service(s)\n3. Select the **Ecommerce — Local** environment",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "API Gateway",
      "description": "Spring Cloud Gateway on :8080. Single entry point that routes all client traffic to downstream services, injects X-Correlation-Id on every request, and handles CORS for MFE origins.\n\nStart: `./gradlew bootRun --args='--spring.profiles.active=local'` from `apps/ecommerce-gateway/`\n\nRoutes:\n- `POST /graphql` → Product Service (:8081)\n- `POST /api/orders`, `GET /api/orders/**` → Order Service (:8082)\n- `GET /api/ai/**` → AI Service (:8083)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Actuator",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Health",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/actuator/health",
                  "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
                  "path": ["actuator", "health"]
                },
                "description": "Returns `{\"status\":\"UP\"}` when the gateway is running."
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Info",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/actuator/info",
